Requirements:
	IITC
	iitc-plugin-drawtools
	iitc-plugin-crosslinks


Inputs:
	spine line - list all drawn line segments to choose from
	set of portals - a circle/polygon and the portals contained within it


Outputs:
	a list of possible plans - number of fields, total area of all fields, list of portals


When a plan is selected, draw using drawtools

